    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "There's been quite a bit of discussion on the bitcoin-dev mailing list. I don't think it's fair to say nobody is working on it. And even if that were true, the solution would be for someone who wants signmessage, to begin working on it.\r\n\r\nI'm not sure how much of a disservice it is. I can't remember the last time I saw signmessage used for what it actually does - everyone who wants it, seems to be assuming things the signatures *don't* prove.",
